Description: Fragment of oval handle of a pottery transport amphora. Clay fine buff. Circular stamp.
Curator's comments: Petrie Diary 1884-5 (EES Archive XVII 47) p. 101a, 5? The better preserved 1925,0119.622a is a more likely identification. Trimmed.
